        dd <ruby>透<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>明<rt>&thinsp;ㆠ丨ㄥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>通<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>光<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㆭ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>丌<rt>&thinsp;˙ㆤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>玻<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄜ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>璃<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㆤˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>真<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄣ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>好<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄜˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>用<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄥ˫/丨ㆲ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>有<rt>&thinsp;ㄨ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>路<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㆦ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>用<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄥ˫/丨ㆲ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>、<ruby>利<rt>&thinsp;ㄌ丨˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>便<rt>&thinsp;ㄅ丨ㄢ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)。
        dd
