        dd <ruby>討<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄜˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>尋<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄨㆤ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>一<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㆵ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>個<rt>&thinsp;ㆤˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>番<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㄢ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>仔<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>火<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㆤˋ/ㄏㆤˋ/ㄏㄜˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>來<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄞˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>用<rt>&thinsp;丨ㆲ˫/丨ㄥ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。

