        dd 類語：聲，～音。音，語～。調，聲～。響，音～。聲音類集：<ruby>巴<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>掌<rt>&thinsp;ㄓㄤˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>乒<rt>&thinsp;ㄆ丨ㄤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>卑<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄟ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>斥<rt>&thinsp;ㄔˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>、<ruby>呵<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄜ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>斥<rt>&thinsp;ㄔˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>、<ruby>鄙<rt>&thinsp;ㄅ丨ˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>斥<rt>&thinsp;ㄔˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>哼<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>呣<rt>&thinsp;ㆬˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，～什麼啊！<ruby>呸<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄟ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，怒斥。<ruby>㕶<rt>&thinsp;ㆭˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>＝嗯，～你說什麼？啐。<ruby>悲<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄟ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>唏<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，～噓。<ruby>唉<rt>&thinsp;ㄞˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>哎<rt>&thinsp;ㄞˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>喲<rt>&thinsp;˙丨ㄛ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>啊<rt>&thinsp;ㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>唷<rt>&thinsp;˙丨ㄛ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>馬<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄚˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>快<rt>&thinsp;ㄎㄨㄞˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>跑<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄠˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：搭啦搭啦。<ruby>馬<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄚˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>叫<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：嘶嘶。嘶噪。蕭蕭(文)。<ruby>人<rt>&thinsp;ㄖㄣˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>促<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄨˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>馬<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄚˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>前<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ㄢˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>進<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄣˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<rt>ㄉㄜㆷ/ㄉㄚㆷ/ㄉㄚ</rt>。<ruby>慢<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄢˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>走<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄡˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：滴哩搭啦滴哩搭啦。<ruby>罵<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>呸<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄟ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>摩<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄛˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>托<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄨㄛ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>車<rt>&thinsp;ㄔㄜ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>緊<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄣˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>急<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>煞<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>車<rt>&thinsp;ㄔㄜ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：突突地。嚓地，～一聲停住。<ruby>摩<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄛˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>擦<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>或壓榨的<ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>音：咭吱咯吱。<ruby>爆<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>炸<rt>&thinsp;ㄓㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：噼噼啪啪(/硼硼砰砰)。畢畢剝剝。砰砰(鎗聲)。轟。地雷炸開。<ruby>爆<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>竹<rt>&thinsp;ㄓㄨˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：硼、砰。<ruby>破<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄛˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>裂<rt>&thinsp;ㄌ丨ㄝˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby><mark>&#xf9d64;</mark><rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>鞭<rt>&thinsp;ㄅ丨ㄢ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>砲/<ruby>炮<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：噼<ruby>啪<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。劈劈<ruby>拍<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>拍。畢畢剝剝。<ruby>冰<rt>&thinsp;ㄅ丨ㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>裂<rt>&thinsp;ㄌ丨ㄝˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：腷腷膊膊。<ruby>雹<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄠˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>子<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄗˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>打<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄚˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>屋<rt>&thinsp;ㄨ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>頂<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨ㄥˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>乒<rt>&thinsp;ㄆ丨ㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>乓<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>跑<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄠˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>步<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄨˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：劈劈<ruby>啪<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>啪<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>砲<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：隆隆。轟隆。──互見爆炸聲。<ruby>碰<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄥˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：見【相碰聲】。見【擊】。「<rt>ㄆㄤ</rt>」。<ruby>皮<rt>&thinsp;ㄆ丨ˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>鞋<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄝˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>啪<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。互見【鞋】。<ruby>不<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄨˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>愉<rt>&thinsp;ㄩˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>快<rt>&thinsp;ㄎㄨㄞˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>的<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄉㄜ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>音<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄣ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：吱呦。<ruby>佩<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄟˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>玉<rt>&thinsp;ㄩˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：丁東。<ruby>紕<rt>&thinsp;ㄆ丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>嗓<rt>&thinsp;ㄙㄤˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>子<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄗˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：沙啞。<ruby>鄙<rt>&thinsp;ㄅ丨ˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>斥<rt>&thinsp;ㄔˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：啐、呸。嘭[擬聲]。　例：～～。敲門聲。<ruby>馬<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄚˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>叫<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：嘶嘶。蕭蕭。<ruby>滅<rt>&thinsp;ㄇ丨ㄝˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>燈<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：噗(/<mark>&#xf907d;</mark>)。<ruby>貓<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄠ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>跳<rt>&thinsp;ㄊ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>落<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄨㄛˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：噗(/撲)騰。叫聲：<ruby>咪<rt>&thinsp;ㄇ丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>嗚<rt>&thinsp;ㄨ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>喵<rt>&thinsp;ㄇ丨ㄠ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。咪。「<rt>ㄋ丨ㄠ</rt>」。<ruby>飛<rt>&thinsp;ㄈㄟ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：扑漉。(鴛鴦帶水飛)。<ruby>貓<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄠ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>跑<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄠˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：貓刺<ruby>棱<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>一下跑了。按：「刺棱」疑非擬聲而是擬態。<ruby>貓<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄠ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>鼠<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄨˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：踢裏拖囉。<ruby>門<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄣˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：乒。梆，敲門聲。<ruby>砰<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>乓<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。乒乓。<ruby>拍<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>拉一聲(門關了)。拍達。吱嘍。<ruby>呀<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。哐。關門聲。<ruby>哐<rt>&thinsp;ㄎㄨㄤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>啷<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。當啷。篤篤(/<ruby>得<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄜˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>得/嗒嗒)。吧嗒。嗒，敲門聲。<ruby>噴<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄣˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>嚏<rt>&thinsp;ㄊ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：見【打噴嚏】。憤怒<ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：呸。<ruby>伐<rt>&thinsp;ㄈㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>木<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄨˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：丁丁。<ruby>飛<rt>&thinsp;ㄈㄟ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>過<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㄨㄛˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>去<rt>&thinsp;ㄑㄩˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：嗖地一聲。潑剌。<ruby>紡<rt>&thinsp;ㄈㄤˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>織<rt>&thinsp;ㄓ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>機<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>的<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄉㄜ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>響<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄤˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：(文)軋軋。類語：戛。<ruby>放<rt>&thinsp;ㄈㄤˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>下<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>話<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>筒<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄨㄥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>喀<rt>&thinsp;ㄎㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>噠<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>表<rt>&thinsp;ㄅ丨ㄠˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>否定<ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>𠮾<rt>&thinsp;ㄟˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>風<rt>&thinsp;ㄈㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：呼呼。嗚嗚。颯颯。蕭蕭(文)。<ruby>簌<rt>&thinsp;ㄙㄨˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>簌。瑟瑟。獵獵(文)。淅淅。修修。<ruby>柔<rt>&thinsp;ㄖㄡ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>兒<rt>&thinsp;ㄦ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>柔<rt>&thinsp;ㄖㄡ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>兒<rt>&thinsp;ㄦ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>地<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄉㄜ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>肉<rt>&thinsp;ㄖㄡ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>肉<rt>&thinsp;ㄖㄡ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>地<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄉㄜ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)[擬音]。拂拂(文)。<ruby>風<rt>&thinsp;ㄈㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>鈴<rt>&thinsp;ㄌ丨ㄥˊ&thinsp;</