;</rt></ruby><ruby>搖<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄠˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>動<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄨㄥˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：吉登，咯登。<ruby>敲<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ㄠ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>門<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄣˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：剝啄(文)。梆梆。砰砰。乒乓(風吹門響)。互見【門聲】。<ruby>瞧<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ㄠˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>不<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄨˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>起<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>語<rt>&thinsp;ㄩˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>氣<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>呸<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄟ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>！<ruby>球<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ㄡˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>洩<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄝˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>氣<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：噗(/<mark>&#xf907d;</mark>)。<ruby>鎗<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ㄤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/槍)<ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<rt>ㄊ丨ㄤ</rt>！砰！<rt>ㄆㄥ</rt>！<rt>ㄆㄤ</rt>！ㄖㄡ一聲鎗(/槍)子兒過去了。<ruby>牆<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ㄤˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>倒<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄠˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>下<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：嘩喇嘩喇(嘩啦)。<ruby>泉<rt>&thinsp;ㄑㄩㄢˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>水<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄨㄟˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：嗚咽。<ruby>犬<rt>&thinsp;ㄑㄩㄢˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>叫<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>狺<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄣˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>狺<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄣˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<mark>&#xf9d63;</mark><mark>&#xf9d63;</mark>。<ruby>吸<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>進<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄣˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>東<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄨㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>西<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄒ丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：忒兒摟(吸麵條，吸鼻涕)。<ruby>細<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>碎<rt>&thinsp;ㄙㄨㄟˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：簌簌。<ruby>細<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>碎<rt>&thinsp;ㄙㄨㄟˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>斷<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄨㄢˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>續<rt>&thinsp