ˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：唧唧。喓喓。咿咿。<ruby>石<rt>&thinsp;ㄕˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：硼硼(相碰)。砰砰。磅磅(衝擊聲)。砰磅，滾落聲。咕咚(大石掉落水中)。<ruby>沙<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>啞<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄚˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：沙沙。<ruby>煞<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>車<rt>&thinsp;ㄔㄜ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>嚓<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。～地一聲摩托車停住了。<ruby>哨<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>嗶<rt>&thinsp;ㄅ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>！。類語：唿哨(口號)。<ruby>鼠<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄨˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>叫<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：(耗子)吱吱。窸窣。<ruby>收<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄡ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>音<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄣ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>機<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：嘎<mark>&#xf8eec;</mark>。(雜音)<ruby>獸<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄡˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>叫<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：咆哮。<ruby>扇<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄢˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>子<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄗˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：刷(/唰)地(打開摺扇)。<ruby>呻<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄣ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>吟<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄣˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：吁<ruby>吁<rt>&thinsp;ㄒㄩˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>噢<rt>&thinsp;ㄩˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>咻<rt>&thinsp;ㄒㄩˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>樹<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄨˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>葉<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄝˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：沙沙。<ruby>摔<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄨㄞ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>碗<rt>&thinsp;ㄨㄢˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>碟<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨ㄝˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>噹<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>水<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄨㄟˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：砰磅(水，石衝擊)。硼硼。(水聲)。渢(文)(水聲)。嘩嘩。<ruby>活<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㄨㄛ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>活<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㄨㄛ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>決<rt>&thinsp;ㄐㄩㄝˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>決<rt>&thinsp;ㄐㄩㄝˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(流動)。濺濺。(文)。潺潺。淙淙。互見【<rt>ㄐ丨ˇ</rt>聲】。汩汩(河水～流入田裏)。<ruby>睡<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄨㄟˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>息<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(<ruby>打<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄚˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>鼾<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄢ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：齁。咕嚕。咕嚕咕嚕。<ruby>自<rt>&thinsp;ㄗˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>言<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄢˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>自<rt>&thinsp;ㄗˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>語<rt>&thinsp;ㄩˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>嘟<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄨ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>囔<rt>&thinsp;ㄋㄤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。嘟嘟囔囔。嘰咕。嘰哩咕嚕。<ruby>砸<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄚˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>破<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄛˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<rt>ㄆㄤ</rt>！。<ruby>嘴<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄨㄟˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>裏<rt>&thinsp;ㄌ丨ˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>含<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄢˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>糊<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：嘟噥。唧噥。<ruby>瓷<rt>&thinsp;ㄘˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>器<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>金<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄣ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>屬<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄨˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>相<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>碰<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄥˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：叮噹。<ruby>嘈<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄠˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>雜<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄚˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：唧拉喳拉。<ruby>嚌<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>嚌嘈嘈。吱喳。<ruby>嘲<rt>&thinsp;ㄓㄠ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>哳。<ruby>啁<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄡ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>哳<rt>&thinsp;ㄓㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。嘰嘰嘎嘎。嘰嘰喳喳。唧唧喳喳。嘁嘁喳喳。唧唧足足。<ruby>雜<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄚˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：吱喳。喳喳。嘩喇。<mark>&#xf9d65;</mark><mark>&#xf9d65;</mark>。嘈雜。<mark>&#xf9d66;</mark><mark>&#xf9d66;</mark>。聒吵。噪雜。喧囂。嘈雜。<ruby>促<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄨˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>馬<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄚˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>咑<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄚ/ㄉㄚˋ/ㄉㄚㆷ/ㄉㄜㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，(北方話理唯一的入聲)。<ruby>搓<rt>&thinsp;ㄔㄨㄛ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>麻<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄚˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>將<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄤˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>牌<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄞˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：嘩啦嘩啦。<ruby>碎<rt>&thinsp;ㄙㄨㄟˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby><mark>&#xf9d64;</mark><rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(物件掉落聲)。<ruby>鵝<rt>&thinsp;ㄜˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>叫<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>哦<rt>&thinsp;ㄜˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>哦。<ruby>鶂<rt>&thinsp;丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>鶂。<ruby>哀<rt>&thinsp;ㄞ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>號<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄠˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：嗷嗷。<ruby>嘔<rt>&thinsp;ㄡˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>吐<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄨˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>哇<rt>&thinsp;ㄨㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>！噦地。喀..<ruby>耳<rt>&thinsp;ㄦˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>刮<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㄨㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>光<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㄨㄤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>/<ruby>聒<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㄨㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>子<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄗˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<rt>ㄅ丨ㄚ</rt>！(打耳刮子)。<ruby>衣<rt>&thinsp;丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>服<rt>&thinsp;ㄈㄨˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>綷<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄨㄟˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>縩<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄞˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>油<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄡˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>花<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>爆<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>開<rt>&thinsp;ㄎㄞ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：滋滋。<ruby>疑<rt>&thinsp;丨ˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>惑<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㄛˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，<ruby>沈<rt>&thinsp;ㄔㄣˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>吟<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄣˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>啊<rt>&thinsp;ㄚˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>那<rt>&thinsp;ㄋㄨㄛˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/哪)。<ruby>嗄<rt>&thinsp;ㄚˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>？<ruby>哦<rt>&thinsp;ㄛˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>？<ruby>嚄<rt>&thinsp;ㄜˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>？<ruby>唵<rt>&thinsp;ㄢˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>噫<rt>&thinsp;丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby>＝咦(驚歎疑惑)。<ruby>疑<rt>&thinsp;丨ˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>訝<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：哦。唵。嗄。哪。嚄。<ruby>儀<rt>&thinsp;丨ˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>仗<rt>&thinsp;ㄓㄤˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>隊<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄨㄟˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby><mark>&#xf9d67;</mark><rt>&thinsp;ㄔㄨㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby><mark>&#xf9d67;</mark><rt>&thinsp;ㄔㄨㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>壓<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>榨<rt>&thinsp;ㄓㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>摩<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄛˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>擦<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：咭吱咯吱。嘎吱咯吱。咯吱(扁擔壓重作響)。嘎吱(柳枝被壓作響)。<ruby>鴨<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>子<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄗˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>叫<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>嘎<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>嘎。咻咻(小鴨聲)。<ruby>呷<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄚˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>呷<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄚˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。小鴨聲。<ruby>葉<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄝˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>子<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄗˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(<ruby>樹<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄨˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>葉<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄝˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：策策。沙沙。瑟瑟。<ruby>搖<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄠˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>動<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄨㄥˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：咭噔咯噔。<ruby>搖<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄠˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>櫓<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄨˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：咿喔。欸乃。啞嘔。<ruby>鴈<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄢˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>叫<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：噰噰。<ruby>燕<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄢˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>子<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄗˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>叫<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：呢喃。<ruby>引<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄣˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>擎<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ㄥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：轟轟。<ruby>羊<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄤˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>叫<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby><mark>&#xf9d79;</mark><rt>&thinsp;ㄇ丨ㄝ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/羋)。<rt>ㄇ丨ˇ</rt>，<mark>&#xf927c;</mark><mark>&#xf927c;</mark>。<ruby>嬰<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>兒<rt>&thinsp;ㄦˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>學<rt>&thinsp;ㄒㄩㄝˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>說<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄨㄛ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>話<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：見【學話】聲。<ruby>應<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄥˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>諾<rt>&thinsp;ㄋㄨㄛˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>𠮾<rt>&thinsp;ㄟˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>唯<rt>&thinsp;ㄨㄟˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。唯唯。是。<ruby>㕶<rt>&thinsp;ㆭ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<mark>&#xf815e;</mark>)。諾諾。應人呼喚之聲，表順從。<ruby>烏<rt>&thinsp;ㄨ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>鴉<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>叫<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>啞<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>啞<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>蛙<rt>&thinsp;ㄨㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>叫<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：嘓嘓。<ruby>玩<rt>&thinsp;ㄨㄢˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>積<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>木<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㄨˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：咚。<ruby>溫<rt>&thinsp;ㄨㄣ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>和<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄜˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>話<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>姁<rt>&thinsp;ㄒㄩˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。音字脫節：諧：昫(言語和靄如老嫗)。→<ruby>呴<rt>&thinsp;ㄒㄩˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>蚊<rt>&thinsp;ㄨㄣˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>子<rt>&thinsp;˙ㄗˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>叫<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：翁翁。轟轟。<ruby>魚<rt>&thinsp;ㄩˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>跳<rt>&thinsp;ㄊ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：撥剌。潑剌(在水中跳躍)。<ruby>魚<rt>&thinsp;ㄩˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>鳥<rt>&thinsp;ㄋ丨ㄠˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聚<rt>&thinsp;ㄐㄩˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>食<rt>&thinsp;ㄕˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>唼<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>喋。<ruby>雨<rt>&thinsp;ㄩˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：嘩嘩(大雨)。淅瀝。刷兒刷兒(小雨)。淅淅。嘩啦啦。霎霎。滴瀝。哩哩啦啦。滴滴答答。刷刷。雨中跑步聲。吧唧吧唧(光著腳板走)。類語：咕唧。<ruby>語<rt>&thinsp;ㄩˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(見說話聲)：喃喃(細語：親密語低語)。<ruby>玉<rt>&thinsp;ㄩˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>瓷<rt>&thinsp;ㄘˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>器<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：丁丁(玉佩)。丁東(玉佩)。東丁(玉聲)。玎玲。<ruby>琤<rt>&thinsp;ㄔㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>琤。玲玲。瑽瑢。瓏璁，玉轡聲。琅璫。叮噹。叮鈴。丁零當郎。<ruby>樂<rt>&thinsp;ㄩㄝˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>器<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>合<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄜˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>奏<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄡˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>嘲<rt>&thinsp;ㄓㄠ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>哳<rt>&thinsp;ㄓㄚˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>鴛<rt>&thinsp;ㄩㄢ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>鴦<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>飛<rt>&thinsp;ㄈㄟ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>起<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：撲漉。<ruby>形<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>容<rt>&thinsp;ㄖㄨㄥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>說<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄨㄛ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>話<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>音<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄣ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>低<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：絮語。呫囁。竊竊私語。嘀(/唙)咕。<ruby>吷<rt>&thinsp;ㄒㄩㄝˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(小聲)。<ruby>形<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>容<rt>&thinsp;ㄖㄨㄥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>音<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄣ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>流<rt>&thinsp;ㄌ丨ㄡˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>利<rt>&thinsp;ㄌ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：嚦嚦。滔滔。侃侃。<ruby>形<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>容<rt>&thinsp;ㄖㄨㄥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>說<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄨㄛ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>話<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>音<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄣ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>高<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㄠ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：大吼。嘹亮。高吭。嘐嘐。喧嘩。喧噪。嚷鬧。悠揚。<ruby>形<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>容<rt>&thinsp;ㄖㄨㄥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>啞<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄚˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：聲嘶。瘖啞。喑啞。<ruby>形<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>容<rt>&thinsp;ㄖㄨㄥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>聲<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>雜<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄚˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：聒<ruby>噪<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。嘩喇嘩喇。喧囂。<mark>&#xf9d66;</mark><mark>&#xf9d66;</mark>。噪雜。嘈雜。嗷嗷。

