        dd  減價拋售。 例：這批貨物銷路太短，總<ruby>得<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄟˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>～為妙。<ruby><mark>&#xffb50;</mark><rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㆵ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(「<ruby>此<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>一<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㆵ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby>」的縮音字)(/<ruby>此<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㆵ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>批<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄨㆤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>貨<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㆤ˪/ㄏㄨㆤ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(泉/漳)，<ruby>銷<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄠ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>路<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㆦ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>真<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄣ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>短<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㆤˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，<ruby>總<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㆲˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>是<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>著<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨ㄜㆷ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>摒<rt>&thinsp;ㄅ丨ㆩ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>斣<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㆦㆶ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(諧：「<ruby>俗<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㆦㆶ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby>」)<ruby>賣<rt>&thinsp;ㆠㄨㆤ˫/ㆠㆤ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>較<rt>&thinsp;ㄎㄚㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>著<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨ㄜㆷ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。(/<ruby>摒<rt>&thinsp;ㄅ丨ㆩ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>斣<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㆦㆶ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>賣<rt>&thinsp;ㆠㄨㆤ˫/ㆠㆤ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>較<rt>&thinsp;ㄎㄚㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>妥<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄜˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>當<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㆲ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)。台類語：<ruby>拍<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄚㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>斣<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㆦㆶ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/俗)<ruby>賣<rt>&thinsp;ㆠㄨㆤ˫/ㆠㆤ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>斣<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㆦㆶ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/俗)<ruby>賣<rt>&thinsp;ㆠㄨㆤ˫/ㆠㆤ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(廉售也、拍賣也)。

