        dd  <ruby>搖<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄜˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>頭<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄠˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，<ruby>㧡<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㆮ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>頭<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄠˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，<ruby>將<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㆲ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>垂<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨ㄣ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>落<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄜㆷ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>丌<rt>&thinsp;˙ㆤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>頭<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄠˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>毛<rt>&thinsp;ㄇㆭˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>㧡<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㆮ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>對<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄨ丨˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>尻<rt>&thinsp;ㄎㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>脊<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄚㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>後<rt>&thinsp;ㄠ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>去<rt>&thinsp;ㄎ丨˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。
